{"tid":167431,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"專家：80% 的 IT 工作可以被自動化取代，情況令人「興奮」","createTime":"2017-03-22T21:52:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-23T09:39:56.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2bc347f36a066e020b211e509d469271a0db734a","tid":167431,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T21:52:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://tomorrowsci.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/IT%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%E8%87%AA%E5%8B%95%E5%8C%96-1-678x381.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftomorrowsci.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F12%2FIT%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E4%25BD%259C%25E8%2587%25AA%25E5%258B%2595%25E5%258C%2596-1-678x381.jpeg&h=b46a4fb2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tomorrowsci.com/technology/%E5%B0%88%E5%AE%B6-80-it%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C-%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E8%A2%AB-%E8%87%AA%E5%8B%95%E5%8C%96-%E5%8F%96%E4%BB%A3%E6%83%85%E6%B3%81%E4%BB%A4%E4%BA%BA%E8%88%88%E5%A5%AE/?utm_source=Page&amp;utm_medium=Direct&amp;utm_campaign=Widget\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftomorrowsci.com%2Ftechnology%2F%25E5%25B0%2588%25E5%25AE%25B6-80-it%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E4%25BD%259C-%25E5%258F%25AF%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E8%25A2%25AB-%25E8%2587%25AA%25E5%258B%2595%25E5%258C%2596-%25E5%258F%2596%25E4%25BB%25A3%25E6%2583%2585%25E6%25B3%2581%25E4%25BB%25A4%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%2588%2588%25E5%25A5%25AE%2F%3Futm_source%3DPage%26utm_medium%3DDirect%26utm_campaign%3DWidget&d=r5q0VKZH5TKX5M4XK8oFTS7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=4fd80238\" target=\"_blank\">https://tomorrowsci.com/technology/%E5%B0%88%E5%AE%B6-80-it%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C-%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E8%A2%AB-%E8%87%AA%E5%8B%95%E5%8C%96-%E5%8F%96%E4%BB%A3%E6%83%85%E6%B3%81%E4%BB%A4%E4%BA%BA%E8%88%88%E5%A5%AE/?utm_source=Page&amp;utm_medium=Direct&amp;utm_campaign=Widget</a><br />\n昇陽電腦（Sun Microsystems）及矽谷創業投資公司柯斯拉創投（Khosla Ventures）的創辦人維諾德&middot;柯斯拉（Vinod Khosla）於舊金山的結構會議（Structure Conference）中斷言，80% 的 IT 工作也可以被人工智慧系統取代。柯斯拉說，「我認為這令人興奮。」<br />\n<br />\n聽眾中大部分是科技公司的資訊總監或其他技術高層。柯斯拉引用了自動化技術公司路坦力（Nutanix）為例，指出人工智慧目前已能自動處理伺服器之間的網路。他亦提到企業軟件公司 Mesosphere，正為各大企業簡化安裝和維護伺服器上的軟件。<br />\n<br />\n柯斯拉認為人工智慧將進軍各地的伺服器和數據中心，取代人類 IT 員工的工作。他解釋，公司保持穩定規模的 IT 部門花費龐大，而這項開銷可以隨著自動化顯著減少。<br />\n<br />\n我們推薦: 馬斯克：機器人將搶走你的工作，而政府必須支付你的工資<br />\n自動化時代<br />\n<br />\n柯斯拉的想法對大眾來說可能難以接受，特別是因為人工智慧將會為很多人帶來失業的噩夢。但柯斯拉安撫聽眾，告訴他們無需擔心，因為「我們都是另外的那 20%，而不是自動化取代的那 80%。」<br />\n<br />\n大部分人認為人工智慧只能取代體力勞動的藍領工作──比如計程車司機或送貨的卡車司機，所以聽眾即使身為 IT 專才，熟悉科技領域的職業趨勢，柯斯拉的預測依然令人甚為驚訝。<br />\n<br />\n但某程度上，這的確令人「興奮」，畢竟機器能做到人類所做的事情是一件令人振奮的事。另外，自動化將令商業過程變得更快、成本更低，為社會經濟帶來某程度上的利益。即使如此，隨之而來的失業潮卻絕對不容忽視。政府及業界領袖必須積極尋找解決方法來維持工人的生計，同時允許科技繼續自然發展。"},{"pid":"bd7cf82da73da3876ab410d2955457d6e9aee3a9","tid":167431,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T21:53:07.000Z","msg":"淘汰IT狗"},{"pid":"a85d4266ac6466bd13b985a07e21de2f74924a91","tid":167431,"uid":78429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T22:43:51.000Z","msg":"AI個價邊有IT咁賤, 又無得用黎出氣<br />\n唔抵"},{"pid":"7beedf95884d040a137bbcd36066d3ee56f9dc24","tid":167431,"uid":37384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T23:13:16.000Z","msg":"等睇香港IT狗狗都冇得做<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"841a554a96b7d3347c05b27a9e4b3d1b766683cc","tid":167431,"uid":59567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T01:30:05.000Z","msg":"it 狗的賤唔係因為做i t related係唔關事一樣係佢地做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"740c24ab7f12a9a7f99ecb67791490e2b6473ba1","tid":167431,"uid":55990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T01:33:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"316aa280ba575ed8cb58930083a2dbd244ee51f5","tid":167431,"uid":11719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T01:40:08.000Z","msg":"IT狗出錯可以屌到IT狗上天花板<br />\nAI出錯唔通入server房屌爆部server咩"},{"pid":"46181907ca23c8d0f29af9682cdef230e10aaed5","tid":167431,"uid":60628,"like":0,"dislike